      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="center" type="letterhead"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3170_0014"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40853">Hotel Saxonia</rs></hi></hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">am <rs type="place" ref="#pmb141471">Potsdamer Platz</rs> und
                        <rs type="place" ref="#pmb36914">Thiergarten</rs></hi></seg><seg rend="center" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb141473"><hi rend="capitals">D. W. Schröder</hi></rs>.</hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print">Fernsprecher:</hi></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="bold">Amt VI. No. 2838.</hi></hi></seg><dateline rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168"><hi rend="capitals"><hi rend="italics">Berlin W.</hi></hi></rs>, den</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1900-03-04">4. März <hi rend="pre-print">1</hi>900</date>.</dateline><seg rend="right" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40854">Königgrätzerstrasse 10</rs>.</hi></seg><salute rend="center">Mein lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Ich beziehe <date when="1900-03-04">heut</date> mein hie<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ige Wohnung, und meine
               Adre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e lautet jetzt: <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40583">De<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>auer Straße 19</rs>.</p><p>Es i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr bedauerlich, daß Du<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreibfaul geworden bi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t.</p><closer>Viele treue Grüße! <lb/>Dein <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
